N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8114.01 - City of Buffalo

State Regulations
(a) Ohio

Street. Ohio Street between Route 5 and Ganson Street. (b) Ganson Street. Ganson Street between Ohio

Street and the General Mills Plant. (c) Seneca Street. Seneca Street between Elm

Street and Louisiana Street. (d) Louisiana Street. Louisiana Street between Seneca Street and South Park

Avenue. (e) South Park Avenue. South Park Avenue between Louisiana Street and South Michigan Street. (f) South Michigan Street. South Michigan

Street between South Park Avenue and the General Mills Plant. (g) Route 266 (Niagara Street). Route 266
(Niagara Street) between IR 190 (exit N11) and Porter Avenue. (h) Genesee Street. Genesee Street between

Route 240 and US Route 62 (Bailey Avenue). (i) Elmwood Avenue. Elmwood Avenue between

Route 198 and Hertel Avenue. (j) Hertel Avenue. Hertel Avenue between Elmwood Avenue to Niagara

Street. (k) Smith Street. Smith

Street between South Park Avenue and Route 16. (l) US Route 62. US Route 62 between Route
130 and Route 354. (m) Route 266. Route 266 between Austin Street and Vulcan Street. (n) Elk Street. Elk Street between US Route
62 and South Park Avenue. Notes
